Physician Rotational Program


To become leaders in today’s ever-changing health care landscape, physicians must be proficient in multiple areas. This program, offered through the office of the chief medical officer, seeks to fill this need. 


 
Email the Physician Rotational Program










































 Menu
			






Contact us




To talk to a program representative or submit your CV for consideration, please email us.







Stand out. Be heard. Be part of the next generation of physician leaders.


Imagine putting your career into overdrive, interacting with top company executives who mentor and bounce ideas off of you. Imagine learning about systems that affect population health at a national level, while continuing to practice medicine and care for individuals.
Humana's Physician Rotational Program is a groundbreaking opportunity unlike any other. This two-year program resides in the office of the chief medical officer and facilitates high-level company exposure and deep, crossfunctional responsibilities. You will be immersed in market-based, core experiences where you will have opportunities to develop innovative solutions to problems you really care about.









Benefits of the Physician Rotational Program



Senior executive mentoring
Development of capabilities in key business areas including strategy, governance, population health improvement, consumer-centered design, financial structures, value-based care, data and analytics and government relations, among others
Competitive pay commensurate with level of training and experience 
Clinical and nonclinical project experiences
The opportunity to continue your clinical practice, if desired 
The chance to be part of a peer network of physician leaders










The ideal candidate



Is board-certified or board-eligible
Has experience practicing independently
Possesses a secondary degree – MBA preferred – MPH or J.D. considered
Is a proven self-motivator who enjoys challenging projects
Is proficient working in a collaborative environment










How the program works


The Physician Rotational Program is a two-year commitment designed to provide comprehensive and detailed understanding of Humana. During the first year, you are immersed in various functional areas across Humana, which provides you with a high-level overview of our organization. During the second year, you are focused on the details at the core of the business.





















